    "The raw outcomes of the experiments are available at https:// github.",
    "com/ tudor groza/ code-for- papers/ tree/ main/ gpt-pheno-cr/ exper iments/ llama2-70B.",
    "The performance of LLAMA2-70B was poor, with efficiency metrics (at both document and mention levels) ranging between 0 and 0.01.",
    "Remarkably, the model returned a mixture of terminologies (HPO IDs, UMLS CUIs, and ICD codes).",
    "We can, hence, conclude that LLAMA2 is not currently fit for HPO-based phenotype recognition without more in-depth analysis of complex prompting techniques."
